page.title: 19LIFE STYLE HOBBIES INTERESTS
page.content: Less than ten but more than five of those questioned listed birdwatching, bowls, Kibworth Band, fishing, keep fit, sailing, snooker and theatre visits. Less than five but more than one recorded aerobics, antique collecting, bingo, boxing, caravaning, computers, cricket, crotching, crosswords, D.I.Y., home decorating, attending dog shows, driving, embroidery, flower arranging, flying, fox hunting, fund raising, glass engraving, goat keeping, helping elderly people, jogging, model making, motor racing, piano playing, horse racing, roller skating, scrabble, shooting, singing, skiing, tapestry, train spotting, watching T.V. and yoga.
